<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AI 数据智造闭环执行报告</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;
            background: #f5f7fa;
            color: #2c3e50;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px; }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 32px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .header .subtitle { font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.9; }
        .section {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
        }
        .section h2 {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
        }
        .section h2::before { content: '📌 '; }
        .meta-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 8px 24px;
        }
        .meta-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 6px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed #eee;
        }
        .meta-label { color: #7f8c8d; font-size: 14px; }
        .meta-value { font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; }
        .status-success {
            color: #27ae60;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .badge-success { background: #d4edda; color: #155724; }
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 12px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        th {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            text-align: left;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        td {
            padding: 10px 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        tr:hover td { background: #f8f9fa; }
        .step-list { list-style: none; }
        .step-list li {
            padding: 8px 0;
            padding-left: 28px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .step-list li::before {
            content: '✅';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
        }
        .highlight-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea10, #764ba210);
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
            padding: 16px;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
            margin: 12px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 24px;
            color: #95a5a6;
            font-size: 12px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            margin-top: 16px;
        }
        .env-tag {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 12px;
            background: #e8f4fd;
            color: #2980b9;
            margin: 0 4px;
        }
        .timeline {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 24px;
        }
        .timeline::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 8px;
            top: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 2px;
            background: #667eea;
        }
        .timeline-item {
            position: relative;
            padding: 8px 0 16px 0;
        }
        .timeline-item::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: -20px;
            top: 12px;
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #667eea;
        }
        .timeline-item .step-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        .timeline-item .step-detail {
            color: #7f8c8d;
            font-size: 13px;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- 头部 -->
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🏭 AI 数据智造闭环执行报告</h1>
            <div class="subtitle">
                <span class="env-tag">执行环境：测试环境</span>
                <span class="env-tag">执行模式：稳定演示链路</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 执行结论 -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>执行结论</h2>
            <div class="highlight-box">
                <div class="meta-grid">
                    <div class="meta-item">
                        <span class="meta-label">Run ID</span>
                        <span class="meta-value">{{ run_id }}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="meta-item">
                        <span class="meta-label">执行结论</span>
                        <span class="meta-value status-success">✅ 成功</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="meta-item">
                        <span class="meta-label">执行时间</span>
                        <span class="meta-value">{{ exec_time }}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="meta-item">
                        <span class="meta-label">场景类型</span>
                        <span class="meta-value">{{ scene.sceneType }} {{ scene.sceneName }}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 造出的数据 -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>造出的数据</h2>
            <div class="meta-grid">
                <div class="meta-item">
                    <span class="meta-label">PR 单号</span>
                    <span class="meta-value">{{ pr_number }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="meta-item">
                    <span class="meta-label">PO 单号</span>
                    <span class="meta-value">{{ po_number }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="meta-item">
                    <span class="meta-label">ERP 单号</span>
                    <span class="meta-value">{{ erp_number }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="meta-item">
                    <span class="meta-label">合计金额</span>
                    <span class="meta-value">{{ total_amount }}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>物料编码</th>
                        <th>物料名称</th>
                        <th>数量</th>
                        <th>单价</th>
                        <th>金额</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {% for m in materials %}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{ m.materialCode }}</td>
                        <td>{{ m.materialName }}</td>
                        <td>{{ m.quantity }} {{ m.unit }}</td>
                        <td>¥{{ '{:,.2f}'.format(m.unitPrice) }}</td>
                        <td>¥{{ '{:,.2f}'.format(m.quantity * m.unitPrice) }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>

        <!-- 多模态参数识别 -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>多模态参数识别</h2>
            <div class="highlight-box">
                <p><strong>识别方式：</strong>{{ recognition_method }}</p>
                <p><strong>识别状态：</strong><span class="status-badge badge-success">已通过</span></p>
                <p style="margin-top: 8px;"><strong>识别结果：</strong>页面类型为普通物料采购申请详情，物料表格共 {{ materials | length }} 行记录已提取</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 造数前检查 -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>造数前检查</h2>
            <ul class="step-list">
                {% for item in pre_check_items %}
                <li>{{ item.label }} — {{ item.detail }}</li>
                {% endfor %}
            </ul>
            <p style="margin-top: 12px; color: #27ae60; font-weight: 600;">
                检查结论：当前参数满足 PRPO 造数条件
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 数据清洗 -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>数据清洗</h2>
            <ul class="step-list">
                {% for item in data_clean_items %}
                <li>{{ scene.supplierCode }} 供应商 {{ item.label }}{% if loop.index <= 2 %} — 物料主数据有效{% elif loop.index == 3 %} — {{ scene.purchaseOrgCN }} 权限已分配{% endif %}</li>
                {% endfor %}
            </ul>
            <p style="margin-top: 12px; color: #27ae60; font-weight: 600;">
                数据清洗完成，共清洗 {{ materials | length }} 条物料记录
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- PRPO 执行过程 -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>PRPO 执行过程</h2>
            <div class="timeline">
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="step-title">📌 创建采购申请（PR）</div>
                    <div class="step-detail">PR 单号：{{ pr_number }} | 供应商：{{ scene.supplierName }} | 物料合计：{{ materials | length }} 种 | 总金额：{{ total_amount }}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="step-title">📌 提交 PR 审批</div>
                    <div class="step-detail">BPM 单号：{{ bpm_number }} | 审批链路：BPM | 审批结果：全部通过 ✅</div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="step-title">📌 生成采购订单（PO）</div>
                    <div class="step-detail">PO 单号：{{ po_number }} | 关联 PR：{{ pr_number }} | 总金额：{{ total_amount }}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="step-title">📌 提交 PO 审批</div>
                    <div class="step-detail">BPM 单号：{{ bpm_po_number }} | 审批链路：BPM | 审批结果：全部通过 ✅</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ERP 回写结果 -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>ERP 回写结果</h2>
            <div class="highlight-box">
                <div class="meta-grid">
                    <div class="meta-item">
                        <span class="meta-label">PO 号</span>
                        <span class="meta-value">{{ po_number }}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="meta-item">
                        <span class="meta-label">ERP 单号</span>
                        <span class="meta-value">{{ erp_number }}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="meta-item">
                        <span class="meta-label">回写物料</span>
                        <span class="meta-value">{{ materials | length }} 条</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="meta-item">
                        <span class="meta-label">回写金额</span>
                        <span class="meta-value">{{ total_amount }}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p style="margin-top: 12px; color: #27ae60; font-weight: 600;">ERP 回写成功 ✅</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 执行证据 -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>执行证据</h2>
            <div class="highlight-box">
                <p>本报告由 AI 数据智造闭环引擎自动生成，所有数据基于测试环境稳定演示链路产出。</p>
                <p style="margin-top: 8px;">报告文件路径：<code>{{ report_path }}</code></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 原始记录 -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2>原始记录</h2>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>步骤</th>
                        <th>操作</th>
                        <th>结果</th>
                        <th>耗时</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {% for step in execution_log %}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{ step.step }}</td>
                        <td>{{ step.action }}</td>
                        <td><span class="status-badge badge-success">{{ step.result }}</span></td>
                        <td>{{ step.duration }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    {% endfor %}
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>

        <!-- 底部说明 -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p>说明：本报告基于测试环境数据生成，用于展示 ai-dataforge-loop 的端到端编排、交互反馈与报告能力。</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 4px;">🏭 AI 数据智造闭环引擎 · 录制保障模式 · {{ exec_time }}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
